irline partners (hotels, restaurants, shopping centres, etc\u2026) where members have the privilege to earn miles whenever they use the services of these partners. To find more please go to\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/corporate.ethiopianairlines.com\/shebamiles\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-sf-ec-immutable=\"\">ShebaMiles<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Follow us on:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/EthiopianAirlines.official\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-27835\" src=\"http:\/\/www.goplacesdigital.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Facebook-Logo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"https:\/\/goplacesdigital.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Facebook-Logo.jpg 225w, https:\/\/goplacesdigital.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Facebook-Logo-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px\" \/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/fly.ethiopian\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-27836\" src=\"http:\/\/www.goplacesdigital.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/instagram.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"https:\/\/goplacesdigital.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/instagram.png 300w, https:\/\/goplacesdigital.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/instagram-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/goplacesdigital.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/instagram-270x270.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px\" \/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/company\/ethiopian-airlines\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-27866\" src=\"https:\/\/goplacesdigital.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/LinkedIn.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 50px) 100vw, 50px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/goplacesdigital.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\